# GeoMerge - Harita Hive Signature Tool
# MIT License - Built by Harita Hive
#
# Seamlessly merge vector or raster layers even with different projections
# Industry-leading merge algorithm with automatic CRS detection and alignment
#
# Features:
# - Multi-format support (SHP, GeoTIFF, GeoJSON, KML)
# - Automatic CRS detection and reprojection
# - Conflict resolution for overlapping geometries
# - Metadata preservation and merging
# - Batch processing capabilities
#
# Usage:
# geomerge --input dir1/ dir2/ --output merged_dataset --format geotiff
# geomerge --vector shp1.shp shp2.shp --output merged.shp --resolve_conflicts
#
# Web Interface: Available at haritahive.com/tools/geomerge